It is by far more accurate, better feel, less recoil, and 1000x better trigger than a factory Glock. It is just as reliable as a factory Glock, and is an amazing carry gun. It has a Zev Tech black on black Fulcrum trigger pad, trigger bar, and ejector housing, which is set up with a 3.0 lb. self defense trigger pull, but can be adjusted to 2 lbs. up too 6 lbs.I also have the pre travel and over travel set up for self defense so it isn't a hair trigger, but it can be adjusted as well to have no pre travel or over travel, but i would not use it for self defense or a carry gun if you choose to set it up with no travel in the trigger. that is competition settings. It also reduces the travel reset of the trigger by 50%. This trigger is super crisp, and breaks better than my Kimber 1911 trigger. By far the bet trigger you can put on a glock. It has a 3.5 Ghost Evo trigger connecter, or I can install the Zev Tech V4 race connector, but will come with both. It has a lightning Strike titanium polished safety plunger with a reduced power plunger spring, or I can install the Zev Tech polished safety plunger, but again it will come with both. I also have 3 standard power springs for the safety plungers. It has a Zev Tech polished, skeletonized, stainless striker pin, with a 6 lb. firing pin spring, but I also have a 4 lb. and 5 lb. firing pin spring for it. ( I highly recommend the 6 lb. spring for a self defense set up.) it has a tungsten recoil assembly with a 16lb. double spring captured, that is 5x heavier than the stock polymer recoil spring, and 2x heavier than a stainless steel recoil assembly, which helps tremendously by reducing lock time by 58% and reducing muzzle flip and felt recoil dramatically. It has a 6lb. Trigger spring, and I have a 5 lb. trigger spring for it as well. It has a KKM Precision stainless match grade barrel that was match fitted by a Master Glock Armorer. It still has enough play to digest all ammo, but locks up tighter for better accuracy. It has a Vickers Tactical Tangodown Mag release, and slide catch, and +1 Pearce Grip Extensions on all 3 mags to make them 10 round mags. It also has marine spring cups for better reliability. It makes it easier to shoot in harsh conditions, and an I-Tac owb button release holster. I have all the factory parts I replaced I.e. barrel, trigger assembly, guide rod etc. It was worth every penny I spent on it, but I'm ready to build something else. I can sen pics of any of the guns if interested.

Bringing the flat shooting, superior ballistic characteristics of the5.45X39 round together with the world's most reliable battle rifle ever made, Arsenal is sure to re-invent history with the addition of this rifle to its product line.

Also, every SGL31 will have Arsenal's upper and lower handguards that are said to be the world's most effective heat dissipating AK handguards on the market due to its stainless steel heat shield. The SGL31 features a hammer forged chrome lined barrel that is built to stand not only the test of time but against any environment or situation encountered. And, with Arsenal's exclusive two stage trigger design, the SGL31 provides a clean and crisp pull when shooting. Available with optional accessories, like the KV-04S scope mount and the four-sided aluminum picatinny rail, the battle tested and battle proven design of the AK-74 becomes the battle rifle of the future in the form of the Arsenal SGL31. Combining these features and many more, like the different stock lengths and colors, the SGL31 sets the standard as the most reliable and accurate battle rifle ever. 

Starting out as a small manufacturer and importer on the west coast, Arsenal, Inc. developed a reputation for building and importing only the highest quality parts. Then, when Arsenal, Inc moved to Las Vegas, NV they transferred that same passion and attention to detail spirit into manufacturing and importing firearms. Now Arsenal serves as full line manufacturer, importer, and developer of the best combat rifles available and the accessories for them.
